385
00:14:03,635 --> 00:14:05,470
Eu entendo.
(RI)

386
00:14:09,474 --> 00:14:10,934
(RI)

387
00:14:11,018 --> 00:14:12,728
Nossa, eu amo a prosa do Palahniuk!

388
00:14:12,811 --> 00:14:14,771
